name: Impakt Wireframe Kit
description:
A free library of ~300 icons, 200+ UI components, ready-made modules and layouts.

Generate, explore, and evaluate more ideas, rapidly.


Takes advantage of modern Figma features:

  • Color and text styles
  • Auto layout and constraints
  • Components and variants
  • Interactive components (beta)


Have suggestions? Leave a comment here or let me know on Twitter.


If you’ve found this library useful, touch the ♡ at the top of the page to show your love. Thanks!


Credits:

  • Inter font family by Rasmus Andersson
  • Feather icons by Cole Bemis
